30#if !defined(ATF_C_CHECK_H)
31#define ATF_C_CHECK_H
32
33#include <stdbool.h>
34
35#include <atf-c/error_fwd.h>
36
37/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
38 * The "atf_check_result" type.
39 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
40
41struct atf_check_result_impl;
42struct atf_check_result {
43 struct atf_check_result_impl *pimpl;
44};
45typedef struct atf_check_result atf_check_result_t;
46
47/* Construtors and destructors */
48void atf_check_result_fini(atf_check_result_t *);
49
50/* Getters */
51const char *atf_check_result_stdout(const atf_check_result_t *);
52const char *atf_check_result_stderr(const atf_check_result_t *);
53bool atf_check_result_exited(const atf_check_result_t *);
54int atf_check_result_exitcode(const atf_check_result_t *);
55bool atf_check_result_signaled(const atf_check_result_t *);
56int atf_check_result_termsig(const atf_check_result_t *);
57
58/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------
59 * Free functions.
60 * --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
61
62atf_error_t atf_check_build_c_o(const char *, const char *,
63 const char *const [],
64 bool *);
65atf_error_t atf_check_build_cpp(const char *, const char *,
66 const char *const [],
67 bool *);
68atf_error_t atf_check_build_cxx_o(const char *, const char *,
69 const char *const [],
70 bool *);
71atf_error_t atf_check_exec_array(const char *const *, atf_check_result_t *);
72
73#endif /* ATF_C_CHECK_H */
